summary: speaking of ps4 from the previous anon im kinda confused does felicia know who peter is under the mask?
question: speaking of ps4 from the previous anon im kinda confused does felicia know who peter is under the mask?
answer:
Maybe, Maybe not. But the way the writers showcased her in most of the scenes, she doesn’t really seem to care much about the man behind the mask. Rather, she is more interested in ‘the spider’. But considering that Peter mentions Felicia’s name to Aunt May early in the game, in one of the conversations, she probably does know but likely isn’t bringing up the topic herself. Assuming she has met May, it boggles my mind as to why the writers of the DLC conveniently forgot to mention that. Like, a conversation between her & Peter, saying that she was sorry for what happened to May, could’ve been nice! 🤷‍♂️

@animesshadow @ladyingreen7

body:
Something’s Gone Wrong




The video has a few seconds of jolty footage before it settles. In the frame is an older teen, obviously sitting on his bedroom covered in fan merch. He takes a breath, and starts speaking.


“If your watching this, something’s gone wrong. Or maybe I just died of old age and I some how kept the biggest secret of my entire life. Anyway, my name is Peter Benjamin Parker at this time of recording I am 18 years old. And I, am the one and only Spider Man. And if this goes badly then that’s why your seeing this.


My parents died a long time ago, so I was raised by my aunt and uncle, Ben and May. Ben died two years ago, logically, it was not my fault. But like everyone, I have irrational thoughts. Ever since it’s just been May and I.


Something I have kept from everyone in my life for a long time, is my identity. Two weeks before Ben died I was bit by a radioactive Spider. I jumped around Queens for a fair few months in, in basically my pyjamas.” He giggles for a moment.


“And then, well, around this time I was approached by Mr. Stark. I was recruited to make up numbers in the Avengers, uh, Walmart parking lot fight.


From here, many of you know the story, I swung around, saved New York from my dates father, um, died regenerated. Went to Europe, didn’t die, saved the those guys. And

We’re back here.


My name is Peter Parker, I am the one and only Spider Man. And if your watching this now, I have died. I like to hope I died saving the world, but knowing me, I probably just had a freak accident with a cyclist after the cool stuff is over.

“ There are so many things I want to apologise for. I’m sorry Liz, I’m sorry Ben, god, May, I’m so sorry.” The teen pauses from his monologue to rub his eye aggressively.

“Mr. Stark, I, I’m sorry for the gray hair and the heart problems. God I’m so sorry but, to everyone. Everyone in the god damn world I am sorry.


“I have failed. God, New York, Queens, Europe, and everyone I couldn’t help. I’m sorry, because by dying, that means I have failed to protect you.


To who ever is out there now, who ever is listening. I’m passing the torch on to you, to the next vigilante mutant, super soldier, martial arts extraordinaire, tin can suit building kid. Anyone can wear the mask.”


The screen fades to black and white text fades on.


‘With great power comes great responsibility. Peter Benjamin Parker.

Peter was killed as Spider Man in a battle.’
